articles.title: Wimbledon champion Vondrousova makes first US Open quarterfinal - WTA Tennis
articles.description: No.9 Marketa Vondrousova kept her cool to rally from a set down to beat unseeded American Peyton Stearns in the fourth round of the US Open.
